  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Underground_GM_Finale
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - Breath and Flesh, both yours. The Guardian does not give its Fragment lightly, and I do not give my praise lightly either.
  - You are an Apprentice no more. From this moment you are an Adept, and the deeper arts open to you.
  - One realm remains. Beyond these caverns lie the Ruins, where the last Fragment sleeps. It is the hardest trial of all, and few who attempt it come back unchanged.
  - Gather your strength and climb to the Ruins. I will meet you where the old world ended. We are so close now.
